==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mrs.
<hw>Mrs.</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <def>The customary abbreviation of
<sig>Mistress</sig> or <sig>Missess</sig> when used as a title of
courtesy, in writing and printing; <as>as, <ex>Mrs.</ex> Clinton is
commonly called by her full name, <person>Hillary Rodham
Clinton</person></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>msasa</ent>⟦br⟧
